        <h2 class="date">Jan 8, 2015</h2>
	<div class="blogbody">
	<h3 class="title">Lecture 2</h3>
	
	<p> In this lecture, we talked about languages as a formal
	mathematical concept, and we talked about how languages are
	modeled. We discussed the expressivity of languages in terms
	of the Chomsky Hierarchy. We started to talk about regular
	languages and finite state automata.

	<p> Here are some <a
	href="http://www.cs.pitt.edu/~hwa/cs2731/01.08.pdf">notes</a>
	from the lecture.
	</div>
	

